data.description: Embrace a refined and serene lifestyle in this beautifully designed Pulte home on a .36-acre lot with scenic hill country views. It boasts a seamless layout perfect for entertaining, featuring a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and extensive storage. The home includes a flexible space for an office or entertainment area, a spacious primary bedroom with a bright ambiance, and an ensuite with a spa-like shower and expansive closet. Privacy is paramount, with no rear neighbors and potential for a custom pool oasis, complemented by a storage shed and playset. Situated in the prestigious Schertz-Cibolo School District. The community offers a state of the art, Amenity Center with pool, playground, and BBQ facilities, this property combines contemporary comforts with community values. It offers a lifestyle of elegance, privacy, and community engagement. Note: Some images are virtually staged to illustrate furnishings and green grass.
